{"title":"台湾乡思","authors":["孙新凯"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":4,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾乡思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙新凯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枇杷树开枇杷花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨梅树结杨梅果；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡鸟叫家乡音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡水流家乡河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相思人唱相思歌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一山橄榄一山桃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一江白帆一溪鹅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油菜开花铺地毯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"榕树撑伞把雨遮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的故乡我的窠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是山中竹一棵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是田里土一勺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是溪边洗衣石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是园中花骨朵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡故乡莫忘我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正月十五闹花灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在异乡点灯火；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月端阳赛龙舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在心中敲起锣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡音乡俗我记着！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是孤雁伤了翅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是船儿丢了舵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是风筝断了线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是浮萍任漂泊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人亲人莫怨我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡的被窝好入梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"异山异水睡不着；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小喝惯闽江水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜂蜜糖汁难解渴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山难阻挡海难隔……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八月十五月似镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镜照玉山芭蕉林；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独在异乡为异客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有明月是乡亲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人伴明月月伴人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴我海边空徘徊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴我病榻苦呻吟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴我共醉消愁酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴我共抒故园情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴我相思伴我梦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一年，骨肉分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天昏昏，海浑浑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月含泪来送行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似慈母提着灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又照夜路又叮咛："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“莫学风筝易断线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要象燕子认家门；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待到十五月圆时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海滩就是望子亭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听着潮声尝月饼……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月悠悠东流水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雁几去几回程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年八月月儿圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手捧月饼泪纷纷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海角天涯游子情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归心似箭箭无弓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉山无心也伤心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火烧芭蕉心不死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游子思归终要归。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘是磁铁儿是针！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}